{"tid":620974,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"Trump tower火災","createTime":"2018-04-08T02:08:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T11:24:11.000Z","uid":90595,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"dc18da7f5c58a3ce105620ab6befe9565099c994","tid":620974,"uid":90595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T02:08:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.foxnews.com/us/2018/04/07/fire-erupts-at-trump-tower-in-new-york-city.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fus%2F2018%2F04%2F07%2Ffire-erupts-at-trump-tower-in-new-york-city.html&d=6sBp%2F%2FOpXbirerEnLVeCCgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=3f5fc5f4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fus%2F2018%2F04%2F07%2Ffire-erupts-at-trump-tower-in-new-york-city.html&h=8d15a234\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.foxnews.com/us/2018/04/07/fire-erupts-at-trump-tower-in-new-york-city.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/search?q=川普大廈&amp;tbm=nws\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Fsearch%3Fq%3D%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E5%A4%A7%E5%BB%88%26tbm%3Dnws&d=6sBp%2F%2FOpXbirerEnLVeCCgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=61ff8aa8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/search?q=川普大廈&amp;tbm=nws</a><br />\n位於美國紐約的川普大廈（Trump Tower）周六晚間發生大火，烈焰跟濃煙從50樓窗口竄出，所幸火災發生時總統川普全家都不在豪宅內，火勢也緊急控制住，但仍傳出有一人重傷，另有三名消防隊員輕傷的不幸消息。<br />\n<br />\n火警傳出不久，人在華府的川普就在推特發文，感謝消防隊員表現得很好，還說失火範圍很小「房子蓋得很好」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43be97da33c9ff48fea22bdb8a62949ad3196e5a","tid":620974,"uid":90595,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T02:10:17.000Z","msg":"@realDonaldTrump<br />\n3 hours ago<br />\n<br />\nFire at Trump Tower is out. Very confined (well built building). Firemen (and women) did a great job. THANK YOU!<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/status/982750459877380096\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FrealDonaldTrump%2Fstatus%2F982750459877380096&d=6sBp%2F%2FOpXbirerEnLVeCCgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=d9f0e6c2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FrealDonaldTrump%2Fstatus%2F982750459877380096&h=78986a12\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/status/982750459877380096</a>"},{"pid":"75e32719e8058da4e253ab9b4bdafa0664eacb1a","tid":620974,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T11:24:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Debimlivinglifemoore/videos/161977635127422/UzpfSTEwMDAwMDUxMzQ0NzcyNjozODcyNTM3MzEyNzg3MzA0/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FDebimlivinglifemoore%2Fvideos%2F161977635127422%2FUzpfSTEwMDAwMDUxMzQ0NzcyNjozODcyNTM3MzEyNzg3MzA0%2F&d=6sBp%2F%2FOpXbirerEnLVeCCgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=f9a56b39\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Debimlivinglifemoore/videos/161977635127422/UzpfSTEwMDAwMDUxMzQ0NzcyNjozODcyNTM3MzEyNzg3MzA0/</a><br />\n見有人直播舊片 推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}